WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 8=

01:50.832 --> 01:53.112
- Your Highness.
- How do you feel?

01:53.433 --> 01:54.313
Much better.

01:55.953 --> 01:56.992
Thank you, Your Highness.

01:58.992 --> 02:00.313
I was just asking.

02:00.832 --> 02:02.433
I'm talking about the monkeys.

02:03.033 --> 02:04.352
Qingyu told me everything.

02:06.073 --> 02:07.153
Let me apply the medicine.

02:09.553 --> 02:10.593
I'll make some tea.

02:17.912 --> 02:19.512
These are old scars.

02:19.873 --> 02:21.632
Medicine won't help much now.

02:24.433 --> 02:26.393
This is Jade Ointment
from the Western Regions.

02:27.472 --> 02:29.672
It contains angelica, chuanxiong root,

02:30.192 --> 02:31.912
peach kernel, safflower,

02:32.952 --> 02:34.153
and pearl powder.

02:34.672 --> 02:36.113
It can reduce scars and soothe skin.

02:37.672 --> 02:38.472
Reduce scars?

02:42.393 --> 02:44.072
Do you find them unsightly?

02:44.072 --> 02:44.752
No.

02:48.072 --> 02:48.873
No.

02:50.713 --> 02:51.952
So, shall we apply it?

03:12.393 --> 03:13.593
Any cooling sensation?

03:16.593 --> 03:20.033
It does feel smooth and cool.

03:22.352 --> 03:23.632
That means it's working.

03:24.873 --> 03:25.912
Apply twice daily.

03:26.313 --> 03:27.313
Within half a month,

03:27.993 --> 03:31.232
these scars will vanish.

03:32.232 --> 03:33.553
It's so effective?

03:35.512 --> 03:37.952
Then, can I have another jar of it?

03:39.433 --> 03:40.752
What for?

03:41.512 --> 03:43.313
You might not even finish one.

03:43.713 --> 03:45.433
I'd like to give one to Qingshuang.

03:45.873 --> 03:48.512
She was also
bitten by monkeys on her arms.

03:49.632 --> 03:50.433
Qingshuang?

03:52.192 --> 03:55.512
Qingyu and Qingshuang grew up with me.

03:55.993 --> 03:58.553
I can't keep this ointment to myself.

04:00.873 --> 04:01.672
Alright.

04:03.072 --> 04:04.593
I'll ask Jin to bring it.

04:05.873 --> 04:06.912
Please don't forget.

04:10.792 --> 04:12.512
Your Highness, the tea is ready.

04:12.912 --> 04:13.713
We are leaving.

04:18.273 --> 04:21.713
Does the Princess Consort
have a maid named Qingshuang?

04:22.833 --> 04:24.633
The Princess Consort has many maids.

04:24.912 --> 04:26.912
Tao, Xing, and Qingyu.

04:27.672 --> 04:31.232
As for Qingshuang,
I can't recall right now.

04:31.513 --> 04:32.593
I'll ask around tomorrow.

04:38.872 --> 04:40.953
My Lady, Devotee Yunji
sent you an invitation

04:40.953 --> 04:42.992
to the Red Sleeve Banquet.

04:43.833 --> 04:44.672
I see.

04:48.073 --> 04:50.552
Devotee Yunji? A spiritual practitioner?

04:50.953 --> 04:52.352
She is the Dowager Consort.

04:52.912 --> 04:54.593
After the late emperor passed away,

04:54.753 --> 04:57.193
Dowager Consort Qin left the palace
and became a spiritual practitioner.

04:57.193 --> 05:00.232
She burns incense, chants sutras,
and prays for the people every day.

05:01.193 --> 05:04.153
Why would a spiritual practitioner
host a banquet?

05:05.112 --> 05:09.073
The Red Sleeve Banquet
honors Lady Lin Tinglan.

05:09.432 --> 05:12.193
The Empress Dowager adores Lady Lin.

05:13.153 --> 05:16.232
As a talented young lady,
instead of being confined indoors,

05:16.232 --> 05:17.352
she travels around

05:17.593 --> 05:19.033
and helps those in need.

05:19.352 --> 05:20.833
People praise her as a heroine.

05:23.513 --> 05:26.073
Come with me tomorrow.

05:27.432 --> 05:28.633
I'm going too?

05:28.872 --> 05:31.833
Dowager Consort Qin
is close to the Empress Dowager.

05:32.593 --> 05:35.593
She's been hosting events
under the pretext of spiritual practice

05:35.953 --> 05:37.593
to form alliances

05:37.633 --> 05:39.033
for the Empress Dowager.

05:40.552 --> 05:42.033
Our family has been in decline

05:42.432 --> 05:44.432
and has never
received an invitation from her,

05:45.073 --> 05:47.472
until you left Lishan Mountain
and married in.

05:47.792 --> 05:50.472
Who do you think she is inviting now?

06:02.912 --> 06:04.472
We haven't seen Lady Lin in ages.

06:04.472 --> 06:05.193
That's right.

06:05.432 --> 06:06.593
Why are we here?

06:07.273 --> 06:08.792
Didn't your third uncle tell you?

06:09.833 --> 06:13.073
Longevity Shop has close ties
to Dowager Consort Qin.

06:31.696 --> 06:34.992
(Lin Tinglan)

07:14.073 --> 07:15.792
What a perfect "Desolate Song".

07:16.073 --> 07:18.912
So deeply moving, it's heartbreaking.

07:19.393 --> 07:20.593
Truly exquisite.

07:20.992 --> 07:25.232
It makes me yearn
for my husband's warm embrace.

07:27.992 --> 07:31.112
You must be
Prince Ding's newlywed bride?

07:37.833 --> 07:40.312
I, Ye Li, pay my respects.

07:41.633 --> 07:42.912
Lady Li from the Ye family.

07:43.753 --> 07:45.073
Princess Li's sister.

07:45.672 --> 07:47.992
I heard she grew up on Lishan Mountain

07:48.273 --> 07:50.312
and returned only to get married.

07:50.792 --> 07:52.432
No wonder we haven't seen her.

07:53.393 --> 07:56.713
Lishan Mountain has been closed
for nearly eight years.

07:57.672 --> 07:58.912
How's the book coming?

07:59.953 --> 08:00.992
Before I left,

08:01.312 --> 08:04.753
Grandfather and tutors were annotating
the Treatise on Rivers and Waterways.

08:05.112 --> 08:07.273
It may take some more time.

08:07.912 --> 08:11.273
I didn't know
you were from Lishan Academy.

08:11.792 --> 08:15.472
Years ago, I read Headmaster Xu's
Hundred Writings,

08:15.953 --> 08:19.112
yet one sentence still puzzles me.

08:20.232 --> 08:22.672
Could you please enlighten me?

08:23.713 --> 08:24.513
My pleasure.

08:25.633 --> 08:27.073
The Hundred Writings states,

08:27.312 --> 08:28.593
"Let knowledge grow.

08:28.713 --> 08:29.753
Leave no one behind."

08:30.153 --> 08:31.953
It means that all people in the world,

08:31.953 --> 08:32.993
regardless of gender

08:32.993 --> 08:34.113
or status,

08:34.513 --> 08:35.873
shall have access to knowledge.

08:36.432 --> 08:38.952
Given this, I'm curious.

08:38.993 --> 08:40.993
Lishan Academy is a leading institution.

08:41.432 --> 08:44.153
Why does it refuse
to accept female disciples?

08:44.312 --> 08:46.072
Headmaster Xu
has written numerous books.

08:46.473 --> 08:49.552
Why does he act against
his own preached doctrines?

08:52.552 --> 08:54.233
Since you enjoy travelogues,

08:54.753 --> 08:57.473
you must have read Journey Among
All Things by Fuyao the Hermit.

08:57.672 --> 08:59.832
Yes. Remarkable work.

09:00.312 --> 09:04.033
Are you aware
that Fuyao the Hermit is a woman?

09:05.393 --> 09:08.832
Lishan Academy has never
denied women entry to its studies.

09:09.832 --> 09:11.353
The commoners often favor sons,

09:11.353 --> 09:12.952
funding education primarily for boys.

09:13.592 --> 09:16.753
Therefore, aspiring male scholars
vastly outnumber female ones.

09:16.952 --> 09:21.192
But Lishan Academy
has female disciples and tutoresses.

09:21.592 --> 09:23.192
Fuyao the Hermit is one of them.

09:23.432 --> 09:24.432
I see.

09:25.712 --> 09:27.393
How ill-informed I was.

09:35.113 --> 09:38.113
I nearly wronged Headmaster Xu.
For penance, I shall drink.

09:40.113 --> 09:42.072
Good.

09:42.633 --> 09:44.832
Misunderstandings ought to be aired out.

09:44.832 --> 09:49.233
Once aired,
grievances vanish like clouds.

09:49.712 --> 09:52.113
Lady Lin acknowledges her error
with an open mind.

09:52.273 --> 09:55.832
I propose we share this toast.

09:55.873 --> 09:57.832
Everyone, raise your cups.

09:58.072 --> 09:59.672
Master Ye speaks well.

10:00.113 --> 10:03.113
I also have a question
for Princess Ding.

10:05.072 --> 10:07.312
The Empress Dowager
admires Lishan Academy.

10:07.552 --> 10:09.353
But right after the late emperor
passed away,

10:09.753 --> 10:12.233
Lishan Academy closed down
to compile texts.

10:12.712 --> 10:18.353
They say you people feared
the Empress Dowager might claim the throne

10:18.952 --> 10:21.993
and found an excuse
to close down the academy.

10:22.552 --> 10:25.353
Is that true?

10:30.113 --> 10:31.993
His Majesty might be young,

10:32.432 --> 10:34.753
but he is steadfast and strategic.

10:35.513 --> 10:38.113
The Empress Dowager
offers her wise advice.

10:38.473 --> 10:40.513
They are of one heart and one mind,

10:40.792 --> 10:43.153
granting Dachu prosperity.

10:43.432 --> 10:46.393
Whoever slanders the Empress Dowager
as attempting to claim the throne

10:46.633 --> 10:49.513
intends to sow discord
between His Majesty

10:49.513 --> 10:50.633
and the Empress Dowager.

10:50.832 --> 10:53.153
Such villains
deserve the gravest punishment.

11:00.353 --> 11:01.832
You are truly eloquent.

11:08.952 --> 11:11.633
Shall we drink together?

11:12.753 --> 11:13.552
Let's drink.

11:14.353 --> 11:16.312
Everyone, raise your cups.

11:17.633 --> 11:18.592
Dig in. Try it.

11:18.592 --> 11:19.393
I'll try it.

11:20.072 --> 11:20.993
This way.

11:20.993 --> 11:21.633
Tasty, right?

11:22.233 --> 11:22.792
And this one.

11:26.233 --> 11:27.952
You're in the mood for food?

11:29.873 --> 11:31.432
Dowager Consort is obviously

11:31.432 --> 11:33.873
siding with the Empress Dowager
against Lishan Academy.

11:34.513 --> 11:36.552
Can't you see this is a trap?

11:36.552 --> 11:37.353
How dare you come?

11:38.192 --> 11:40.072
She invited me. So I came.

11:40.353 --> 11:43.792
Master Ye, this lotus lamp won't light.

11:43.993 --> 11:44.792
Is that so?

11:44.792 --> 11:45.753
- Let me see.
- Look.

11:46.552 --> 11:47.952
I'll come shortly.

11:47.952 --> 11:48.473
Hurry up.

11:48.473 --> 11:49.952
Be cautious.

11:56.912 --> 11:58.912
What I'm holding is a Four Flavors Puff,

11:59.552 --> 12:01.273
stuffed with
seasonal fruits and flowers.

12:01.353 --> 12:04.192
The crust is made
with rare wild cliff honey.

12:04.633 --> 12:06.592
This honey is incredibly precious.

12:06.712 --> 12:08.552
A single jar costs 100 qian of silver.

12:09.233 --> 12:11.952
You endured years of hardship
on the mountain.

12:12.353 --> 12:14.633
I bet you haven't
enjoyed such luxuries for years.

12:17.513 --> 12:19.832
Here, dig in. It's all yours.

12:22.952 --> 12:24.873
Has living on the mountain

12:25.552 --> 12:27.672
made you forget your manners?

12:31.873 --> 12:32.753
What's wrong?

12:33.792 --> 12:36.952
You have black sesame seeds
stuck between your teeth.

12:37.712 --> 12:38.513
Thank you.

12:39.072 --> 12:40.592
Check my teeth. Where is it?

12:42.633 --> 12:43.473
I don't see it.

12:43.473 --> 12:44.672
Look carefully.

12:49.993 --> 12:50.952
Please spare me.

12:52.192 --> 12:52.993
It's fine.

12:56.393 --> 12:57.952
It won't come off so easily.

12:57.952 --> 13:00.033
May I take you to clean it up?

13:01.592 --> 13:02.473
Wait here.

13:02.792 --> 13:03.592
Alright.

13:06.273 --> 13:08.633
Don't be mad, Your Highness.
Have some pastries.

13:09.312 --> 13:10.113
Take them away.

13:10.592 --> 13:13.873
Never serve me
anything with sesame in public again.

13:14.353 --> 13:15.153
Yes, Your Highness.

13:23.192 --> 13:24.912
Not the milk cakes though.

13:24.993 --> 13:26.473
They're sesame-free.

13:50.273 --> 13:51.552
Bring Ma'am Zhu.

13:51.792 --> 13:52.552
Yes, Your Highness.

14:13.273 --> 14:14.993
Here we are, Your Highness.

14:28.273 --> 14:30.753
There's nothing here. How do I rinse it?

14:48.633 --> 14:49.712
Are you mad at me?

14:52.873 --> 14:56.353
Li, let me explain.

14:56.633 --> 14:58.552
I didn't mean
to break off our engagement.

14:58.552 --> 15:01.153
They forced me to.

15:01.792 --> 15:04.432
They said that Guo Jin
had become suspicious of me.

15:05.353 --> 15:08.633
Marrying you would be
dragging you down with me.

15:09.993 --> 15:13.033
I thought you could stay on the mountain

15:13.672 --> 15:14.873
if I broke off the marriage.

15:16.993 --> 15:21.873
But Guo Jin betrothed you
to that disabled man.

15:25.513 --> 15:26.912
What are you trying to say?

15:28.393 --> 15:29.192
Li.

15:31.912 --> 15:32.912
Let's run away.

15:34.633 --> 15:35.432
Run away?

15:36.993 --> 15:37.792
Yes.

15:38.832 --> 15:39.633
Run away.

15:41.873 --> 15:44.993
I've had this idea for too long.

15:47.072 --> 15:48.072
On your wedding day,

15:49.993 --> 15:51.873
I saw you step into
another man's carriage

15:52.792 --> 15:54.273
in your bridal gown.

15:56.952 --> 16:00.353
That's when the thought
took root in my mind.

16:05.712 --> 16:07.473
I want to take you
to ride out of the city,

16:09.312 --> 16:10.912
through the Eastern Market,

16:12.792 --> 16:14.153
out past the city gates,

16:16.113 --> 16:18.033
and along the winding mountain path,

16:20.153 --> 16:21.153
back to Lishan Mountain.

16:25.592 --> 16:26.792
And if not Lishan Mountain,

16:27.273 --> 16:28.113
then Eastern Peak,

16:28.832 --> 16:29.832
or the borderlands,

16:31.273 --> 16:32.192
or Cangbei.

16:34.792 --> 16:35.672
Anywhere is fine,

16:37.633 --> 16:38.592
as long as you're there.

16:41.712 --> 16:42.912
But you didn't do that.

16:49.513 --> 16:50.312
That's right.

16:52.952 --> 16:54.273
Because I got scared.

16:55.712 --> 16:58.113
I knew we couldn't
make it back to Lishan Mountain.

16:58.832 --> 17:01.192
We couldn't even escape that alley.

17:09.552 --> 17:11.152
You haven't changed one bit.

17:11.792 --> 17:13.312
Still the same as before.

17:14.072 --> 17:16.792
Cowardly and hypocritical.

17:17.312 --> 17:20.592
You always hide your ugliness
behind high-sounding words.

17:20.592 --> 17:21.713
And after a while,

17:22.673 --> 17:26.953
you actually start believing
that you're honest and righteous.

17:28.392 --> 17:29.352
Prince Li.

17:30.552 --> 17:34.632
Don't you find yourself ridiculous
when you say these things?

17:46.193 --> 17:47.072
Mo Jingli,

17:48.392 --> 17:50.552
I genuinely despise you.

17:51.312 --> 17:52.792
So stay away from me.

18:00.352 --> 18:02.473
Ma'am, where are they?

18:02.872 --> 18:03.632
Li.

18:05.112 --> 18:06.433
I hear voices up ahead.

18:06.753 --> 18:07.792
Shall we take a look?

18:07.953 --> 18:08.792
Let's go.

18:09.392 --> 18:10.993
No, I don't believe it.

18:11.112 --> 18:13.753
If you truly didn't care
and truly loathed me,

18:13.753 --> 18:15.233
why did you kill Lu Changfu?

18:18.832 --> 18:21.632
You knew
my precarious position at court.

18:22.392 --> 18:23.872
So you killed Lu Changfu

18:24.552 --> 18:28.552
to sow discord between His Majesty
and the Empress Dowager, right?

18:30.112 --> 18:33.392
You can't fool me.
I know your tactics all too well.

18:34.312 --> 18:37.233
So you still care about me.

18:40.152 --> 18:41.513
I killed Lu Changfu

18:42.473 --> 18:43.552
not for you,

18:44.872 --> 18:46.473
but for Lishan Academy.

18:47.112 --> 18:49.392
He owed Lishan Academy seven lives.

18:49.392 --> 18:50.913
He had to pay with his life.

18:51.552 --> 18:53.112
It had nothing to do with you.

18:56.273 --> 18:57.392
Ye Li, stop.

18:59.753 --> 19:01.312
Take one more step forward,

19:02.072 --> 19:03.513
and I will jump into this pond.

19:04.152 --> 19:06.872
You know I can't swim.

19:17.112 --> 19:19.753
Let go of me. Let me die.

19:20.433 --> 19:22.713
Let me go.

19:23.433 --> 19:25.632
Let me die.

19:26.792 --> 19:32.592
(Cicadas always seem to want
attention by making noise,)

19:33.352 --> 19:35.872
(as if that's the whole point
of their existence.)

19:36.913 --> 19:39.592
(But the membranes
they use to make noise are so thin)

19:40.152 --> 19:42.913
(that the slightest strain
tears them apart.)

19:44.592 --> 19:45.513
(Mo Jingli.)

19:46.632 --> 19:48.473
(You are exactly like those cicadas.)

20:32.552 --> 20:33.352
Master Gu.

20:33.360 --> 20:35.472
(Gu Zheng)

20:36.033 --> 20:36.832
Long time no see.

20:39.152 --> 20:40.352
General Mo.

20:42.112 --> 20:45.473
No, Prince Ding, I should say.

20:45.713 --> 20:48.673
What brings you to visit
an old man like me?

20:50.673 --> 20:53.152
I've come to request your assistance.

20:54.273 --> 20:55.472
You joined the officialdom?

20:57.152 --> 20:58.544
Prefect of Jingzhao Prefecture.

21:06.753 --> 21:10.832
Master Gu, you are
just like a pearl buried in dust.

21:11.713 --> 21:13.433
The people yearn for true governance.

21:13.753 --> 21:14.913
But shadow lingers

21:15.112 --> 21:16.273
above the imperial court.

21:16.713 --> 21:21.792
If you'd take up the brush of justice
and join me in sweeping away

21:22.312 --> 21:24.233
centuries of corruption

21:24.433 --> 21:25.513
and purging the world

21:25.513 --> 21:26.792
of its filth,

21:27.152 --> 21:29.513
then we can build a legacy

21:29.993 --> 21:33.872
that shakes heaven and earth
and saves the people.

21:34.513 --> 21:38.433
Where did you learn those fancy words,
just to disgust me?

21:38.673 --> 21:42.993
I paid a scholar on the way here.
He wrote it on the spot.

21:43.152 --> 21:44.713
I bet you didn't pay him well.

21:44.713 --> 21:46.713
The flattery is devoid of sincerity.

21:46.713 --> 21:47.913
Get real with me.

21:51.993 --> 21:53.273
I intend to rectify the wrongs,

21:54.152 --> 21:55.592
restore my family's honor,

21:56.193 --> 21:57.552
vindicate the Heiyun Cavalry,

21:58.953 --> 22:02.552
and seek justice
for my deceased elder brother.

22:03.152 --> 22:04.513
The cost of securing my services

22:04.552 --> 22:06.713
might be too high for you.

22:07.552 --> 22:10.072
Why don't you spell it out?

22:17.112 --> 22:20.053
I want to engrave the denunciation
from eight years ago

22:20.053 --> 22:22.993
on Marquis Muyang's tombstone.

22:31.513 --> 22:32.433
Deal.

22:34.273 --> 22:35.120
On the fifth day of next month,

22:35.120 --> 22:36.673
the Minister of Rites will
hold a feast for his grandson.

22:36.673 --> 22:39.568
At the Heaven-worshipping ceremony
three years ago, entrusted by you,

22:39.568 --> 22:40.872
he offered incense for you.

22:40.953 --> 22:42.273
You sought his help

22:42.273 --> 22:43.792
and wished for eighteen sons.

22:43.792 --> 22:45.152
It became a running joke.

22:45.152 --> 22:47.513
It went perfectly,
but we need a follow-up.

22:47.953 --> 22:49.312
Your Highness should thank him.

22:49.312 --> 22:52.312
The gift shouldn't be too modest.
Nor should it be excessive.

22:53.473 --> 22:56.233
I have prepared a set
of gold lock, bracelet, and anklet

22:56.233 --> 22:58.993
with auspicious cloud patterns

22:58.993 --> 23:00.433
and a pair of jade pendants.

23:01.072 --> 23:04.913
At the banquet, you'd best
play the zither to congratulate them.

23:05.592 --> 23:08.473
On the eighth day of next month,
there's a polo match at Yunjing Garden.

23:08.473 --> 23:09.832
Yuan Changkong will be there.

23:09.913 --> 23:11.673
You've been on bad terms for years.

23:11.753 --> 23:13.513
Make sure you argue with him.

23:13.513 --> 23:15.673
Get physical if possible

23:15.673 --> 23:17.072
till you have bruises on the face.

23:21.233 --> 23:22.673
- On the fifteenth day...
- I won't go.

23:24.473 --> 23:25.433
Which one?

23:26.513 --> 23:27.713
None of them.

23:30.513 --> 23:32.273
But you must show up, Your Highness.

23:32.953 --> 23:35.312
You haven't joined any banquets
in over a month.

23:35.312 --> 23:37.312
Do you know what people say about you?

23:37.312 --> 23:39.913
They say that you've settled down
since you got married,

23:40.792 --> 23:44.913
casting aside your frivolous ways
and becoming composed.

23:47.673 --> 23:52.312
But why would the son
of a former crown prince be so composed?

23:58.312 --> 23:59.913
Then what should I do?

24:03.592 --> 24:04.913
Be as you were before.

24:09.592 --> 24:11.193
As I was before?

24:13.872 --> 24:14.753
Play the zither,

24:14.753 --> 24:15.552
get drunk,

24:15.552 --> 24:16.473
act like a madman,

24:18.673 --> 24:20.592
and get into brawls with others.

24:22.312 --> 24:23.233
Better still,

24:24.993 --> 24:26.753
tear my clothes,

24:27.513 --> 24:28.872
bruise my face,

24:30.193 --> 24:33.913
then parade that very image
of degeneracy at court,

24:34.513 --> 24:38.473
inciting revulsion from all,
and making myself the laughingstock.

24:39.273 --> 24:40.312
That's exactly it.

24:59.792 --> 25:01.673
I know your heart harbors bitterness.

25:02.392 --> 25:03.632
But this is the only way

25:04.352 --> 25:07.473
to convince the Empress Dowager
that you're just a decadent libertine

25:07.792 --> 25:11.352
instead of someone consumed by hatred.

25:13.233 --> 25:14.632
And only then...

25:22.832 --> 25:24.673
can you survive.

25:25.673 --> 25:29.033
Only then can your family survive.

25:42.193 --> 25:46.832
Then I shall continue
making the arrangements for you.

25:53.792 --> 25:55.312
Since Your Highness feels troubled,

25:56.433 --> 25:57.193
let off some steam

25:58.513 --> 25:59.913
at the Yinshan Mountain Retreat

26:02.273 --> 26:03.713
(Visit Yinshan Mountain Retreat)
on the day after tomorrow.

26:40.152 --> 26:42.112
Your Highness.

26:42.112 --> 26:43.993
Master Zhu's stone flowers have bloomed.

26:44.473 --> 26:45.392
Really?

26:45.792 --> 26:46.632
Take a look.

26:47.832 --> 26:48.433
Your Highness.

26:49.632 --> 26:51.352
Tao and I tend to them meticulously.

26:51.352 --> 26:52.953
We water them with the dew

26:52.953 --> 26:54.953
from the grass tips
before the sun rises.

26:55.473 --> 26:56.913
Surely they sense our devotion.

26:57.033 --> 26:58.233
So they bloom to delight us.

26:58.592 --> 26:59.913
Your Highness promised

26:59.913 --> 27:01.352
to treat us to a feast

27:01.352 --> 27:02.592
if the stone flower blooms.

27:02.592 --> 27:03.953
Are you true to your word?

27:04.033 --> 27:04.832
Of course.

27:05.592 --> 27:06.953
That's great!

27:06.953 --> 27:07.953
- Thank you, Your Highness.
- Thank you, Your Highness.

27:09.913 --> 27:10.713
Your Highness.

27:11.473 --> 27:12.392
What happened outside?

27:12.953 --> 27:13.993
Just on my way here,

27:14.033 --> 27:17.953
I noticed many strong men
hauling furniture around,

27:17.953 --> 27:19.713
as if installing new furnishings.

27:24.352 --> 27:24.953
Hurry up.

27:24.953 --> 27:25.713
Be careful.

27:25.713 --> 27:27.112
Don't chip anything. Hurry up.

27:42.513 --> 27:45.552
Are you renovating the mansion?
Why did you buy so many things?

27:46.592 --> 27:47.632
Ask your third uncle.

27:55.872 --> 27:57.392
Higher.

27:58.392 --> 27:59.072
Be careful.

28:00.033 --> 28:02.352
My screen with mother-of-pearl Inlay.

28:02.352 --> 28:03.352
Be careful, okay?

28:04.112 --> 28:05.033
Watch it.

28:05.993 --> 28:06.832
Uncle Wenshen.

28:07.273 --> 28:08.033
Li.

28:09.832 --> 28:10.953
Your timing is perfect.

28:10.953 --> 28:12.552
Take this inside the room.

28:13.072 --> 28:14.592
Let's get this one. It's light.

28:14.592 --> 28:16.233
Come on, give me a hand.

28:16.953 --> 28:18.033
What a commotion.

28:18.152 --> 28:19.792
You emptied the entire Longevity Shop?

28:20.072 --> 28:22.792
Of course not.
These are just daily necessities.

28:22.913 --> 28:24.953
I can't stay at your place forever.

28:24.953 --> 28:26.513
I have so much work at the shop.

28:26.513 --> 28:29.233
Those devotees are waiting for me
to pray for them.

28:29.673 --> 28:30.753
How long will you stay?

28:31.953 --> 28:33.152
Let's start with two months.

28:33.473 --> 28:34.713
That's way too long.

28:35.953 --> 28:37.632
How heartless can you be?

28:37.632 --> 28:39.592
Who treats you best
in the entire Ye family?

28:39.592 --> 28:40.632
It's me, right?

28:40.792 --> 28:41.993
Can't I stay for a few days?

28:42.312 --> 28:43.033
Why can't I...

28:48.832 --> 28:49.632
What's that?

28:50.033 --> 28:53.433
This... is the Celestial Maiden.

28:54.513 --> 28:57.792
Loot at her. Her beaded necklace
is magnificent, right?

28:59.392 --> 29:02.193
Li, you are now
the esteemed Princess Consort.

29:02.592 --> 29:04.953
Your daily provisions
must reflect that status.

29:05.473 --> 29:06.392
From what I see now,

29:06.392 --> 29:08.792
my apprentices at the shop
live better than you.

29:08.792 --> 29:09.792
That won't do.

29:09.792 --> 29:10.872
The bed is stiff.

29:10.872 --> 29:12.233
The desk is small. The window...

29:12.233 --> 29:13.632
What about the window?

29:14.372 --> 29:16.072
It lets in far too much light.

29:16.072 --> 29:18.513
It's too transparent.
It disturbs my sleep.

29:18.872 --> 29:20.993
Bad sleep gives me awful headaches.

29:20.993 --> 29:22.713
I'll do it myself. Let it be.

29:22.713 --> 29:24.352
Tell you what, I brought some fine tea.

29:24.352 --> 29:25.112
Come on in.

29:37.168 --> 29:38.953
(Basking in Grace)

29:38.953 --> 29:40.112
Green Plum Prelude.

29:47.233 --> 29:48.632
You just can't let it go.

29:49.592 --> 29:51.832
Ye Li, you've gone too far this time.

29:52.112 --> 29:53.993
Your Highness, please calm down.

29:54.312 --> 29:56.273
They merely had an engagement years ago.

29:56.273 --> 29:57.552
It's all in the past.

29:57.872 --> 29:58.913
How is that in the past?

29:59.233 --> 30:00.953
They're still meeting in private.

30:00.953 --> 30:02.352
Were you blind?

30:02.352 --> 30:03.632
So what if they meet?

30:03.832 --> 30:05.392
It's the Empress Dowager's decree.

30:05.673 --> 30:06.513
They are

30:06.513 --> 30:07.433
both married.

30:07.592 --> 30:10.592
She won't let them off
if they do anything inappropriate.

30:11.312 --> 30:12.832
I can't swallow this insult.

30:14.673 --> 30:16.193
What can you do?

30:18.513 --> 30:19.513
Someone has to die.

30:20.273 --> 30:21.072
Your husband?

30:21.572 --> 30:22.993
Y-You want to kill Prince Li?

30:23.273 --> 30:25.152
That's a deadly crime.

30:25.433 --> 30:26.392
What nonsense.

30:26.632 --> 30:27.632
I'm talking about Ye Li.

30:28.513 --> 30:33.033
Your Highness, we can't just
kill someone like in the storybook.

30:33.433 --> 30:34.273
How do you kill her?

30:34.513 --> 30:36.193
She is Princess Ding.

30:36.433 --> 30:37.792
Who would take such a job?

30:38.513 --> 30:42.112
Let me make you something to eat.
Stop overthinking this.

30:47.273 --> 30:49.832
So what if she's Princess Ding?
I'm Princess Li.

30:50.592 --> 30:51.832
I'll find a way.

30:52.080 --> 30:53.572
(Groceries)

31:07.888 --> 31:09.936
(Han Mingxi)

31:12.792 --> 31:15.273
My Lady, are you looking
for someone to hire?

31:17.713 --> 31:18.473
Your price range?

31:19.273 --> 31:21.792
It depends on the distance.

31:21.792 --> 31:22.673
We have many workers.

31:23.033 --> 31:24.673
How many people do you need?

31:24.832 --> 31:26.993
The job takes place inside the capital.

31:27.392 --> 31:28.312
Inside the capital?

31:28.552 --> 31:29.072
Yes.

31:30.152 --> 31:31.913
The headcount doesn't matter

31:32.233 --> 31:33.713
as long as the job is done neatly.

31:33.913 --> 31:34.792
Rest assured.

31:34.913 --> 31:37.033
Our men always carry out tasks cleanly.

31:37.673 --> 31:38.673
Good.

31:39.552 --> 31:42.033
Bring the target before me,
and you shall be rewarded.

31:42.233 --> 31:43.632
Bring the target before you?

31:43.673 --> 31:45.872
Yes. Do not strike yet.

31:45.993 --> 31:47.592
Wait for my command.

31:47.673 --> 31:50.072
My Lady, what kind of workers
are you seeking?

31:50.753 --> 31:51.592
Assassins.

31:52.473 --> 31:53.273
Assassins?

31:53.713 --> 31:55.193
We escort goods for a living.

31:55.352 --> 31:56.753
We can help collect debts.

31:57.033 --> 31:58.872
But murder is out of the question.

31:59.152 --> 31:59.673
But...

31:59.673 --> 32:00.513
Please leave.

32:00.592 --> 32:02.673
Or I'll report you to the authorities.

32:02.792 --> 32:03.312
I...

32:05.993 --> 32:07.072
What's the world coming to?

32:10.993 --> 32:12.193
Need an assassin?

32:24.152 --> 32:26.312
Why do we have to talk here?

32:26.592 --> 32:29.832
The most dangerous place
is often the safest.

32:30.433 --> 32:32.473
It's the biggest restaurant
in the capital.

32:32.473 --> 32:38.112
No one would imagine
that under broad daylight,

32:38.273 --> 32:42.953
someone would discuss
a murder deal here.

32:46.152 --> 32:48.033
Why do we have to talk like this?

32:48.552 --> 32:49.953
For our safety,

32:50.033 --> 32:52.993
it's best if we never
see each other's faces.

32:54.352 --> 32:55.552
Who do you want to kill?

32:57.713 --> 32:58.513
Don't say it.

33:04.273 --> 33:05.072
Write it down.

33:12.336 --> 33:13.584
(Princess Ding, Ye Li)

33:16.513 --> 33:17.832
Can you afford my price?

33:18.913 --> 33:20.713
Of course. Name your price.

33:22.672 --> 33:23.312
(Five thousand guan)

33:25.473 --> 33:26.673
So much?

33:30.433 --> 33:31.033
Deal.

33:31.872 --> 33:33.112
Then it's settled.

33:33.233 --> 33:34.312
You're killing her now?

33:34.312 --> 33:35.112
Turn around.

33:38.592 --> 33:41.392
I have some arrangements to make.

33:44.753 --> 33:45.993
I have one more condition.

33:48.872 --> 33:49.632
I'm listening.

33:49.753 --> 33:52.352
Capture her alive and bring her to me.

33:52.592 --> 33:56.193
I am an assassin, not a kidnapper.

33:56.233 --> 33:57.273
You too, turn around.

33:59.592 --> 34:00.513
I know.

34:01.792 --> 34:02.673
It's just that...

34:03.832 --> 34:04.592
I...

34:04.792 --> 34:06.072
You wish to do it yourself?

34:08.913 --> 34:11.433
Yes. Exactly.

34:11.752 --> 34:12.953
So I want her alive.

34:13.112 --> 34:15.272
That increases the price.

34:15.953 --> 34:17.833
Get it done and you'll get double.

34:17.833 --> 34:18.552
Deal.

34:19.272 --> 34:20.473
Is there anything else?

34:20.953 --> 34:21.712
No.

34:31.353 --> 34:32.473
Won't you take the front door?

34:32.473 --> 34:35.833
I'm an assassin.
I never take the front door.

34:42.993 --> 34:43.913
What an expert.

34:58.192 --> 34:59.592
Look where you're going.

35:52.473 --> 35:55.033
You've been busy all day.
Have some lychees and rest.

35:55.513 --> 35:59.393
The imperial physician says lychees
replenish energy and relieve fatigue.

35:59.552 --> 36:01.152
A short break will do you good.

36:01.913 --> 36:03.433
I didn't realize it.

36:04.313 --> 36:06.873
I am somewhat tired, indeed.

36:17.672 --> 36:19.793
Crystal clear and sweet. Very good.

36:22.793 --> 36:24.473
Documents pile up like mountains.

36:24.632 --> 36:26.232
Why bind yourself so?

36:26.873 --> 36:28.552
You're exhausting yourself here.

36:28.793 --> 36:32.313
But that young child
may not appreciate your kindness.

36:34.473 --> 36:36.072
What have you heard again?

36:38.152 --> 36:42.112
I heard Prince Ding requested a man
from His Majesty. Gu Zheng.

36:43.033 --> 36:45.353
His Majesty has already released him.

36:49.313 --> 36:50.112
Gu Zheng.

36:52.313 --> 36:53.833
He joined the court 14 years ago.

36:54.192 --> 36:57.712
The longstanding cases he solved
proved him capable.

36:57.712 --> 36:59.024
In the first year of the Xide Era,

36:59.152 --> 37:02.793
Marquis Muyang discovered some
Lishan Academy disciples plotted rebellion

37:02.913 --> 37:04.913
and sent Lu Changfu to arrest them.

37:05.353 --> 37:07.473
But those disciples refused to confess.

37:07.672 --> 37:10.473
So Lu Changfu burned them alive.

37:11.953 --> 37:15.192
Gu Zheng learned of this
and wrote to impeach Marquis Muyang.

37:15.192 --> 37:18.072
His superiors
intercepted the denunciation.

37:18.353 --> 37:20.513
Then he criticized the court
outside the palace,

37:20.552 --> 37:22.192
insulting you and Marquis Muyang,

37:22.192 --> 37:23.672
and was sentenced to death.

37:23.833 --> 37:26.752
But both execution attempts
met with obstacles.

37:27.393 --> 37:30.353
First, lightning struck an ancient tree
in the Marquis Muyang's mansion.

37:30.913 --> 37:33.152
Later, the executioner broke his arm.

37:34.473 --> 37:37.712
You declared that heaven shows mercy
to the living

37:38.232 --> 37:41.232
and that he may carry divine blessings.

37:41.272 --> 37:42.993
You spared his life
and kept him in jail.

37:43.833 --> 37:45.793
Now, eight years have slipped by.

37:46.152 --> 37:47.793
He still refuses to confess

37:47.993 --> 37:49.752
and keeps cursing every day.

37:50.152 --> 37:53.592
His Majesty released such a man

37:53.632 --> 37:57.552
and reinstated him to his position
in the Jingzhao Prefecture.

37:58.873 --> 38:01.513
His Majesty is just a child, after all.

38:03.712 --> 38:04.793
You're right.

38:05.712 --> 38:07.993
Perhaps His Majesty values his ability

38:08.433 --> 38:09.993
and doesn't intend to upset you.

38:12.873 --> 38:16.873
Yanqi is young and hasn't learned
to be thoughtful.

38:17.632 --> 38:18.953
I will guide him.

38:26.256 --> 38:28.944
(Ye Mansion)

38:41.313 --> 38:45.672
♪The towering Lishan Mountain♪

38:48.112 --> 38:52.793
♪Rises into the sky♪

38:55.672 --> 39:00.272
♪The mighty Lishui River♪

39:01.712 --> 39:05.513
♪Flows ever east♪

39:15.592 --> 39:19.953
♪The towering Lishan Mountain♪

39:22.393 --> 39:27.072
♪Rises into the sky♪

39:29.953 --> 39:34.552
♪The mighty Lishui River♪

39:35.993 --> 39:40.433
♪Flows ever east♪

39:55.112 --> 39:59.793
♪Rises into the sky♪

40:02.672 --> 40:07.272
♪The mighty Lishui River♪

40:14.993 --> 40:16.833
Wanzhou, is that you?

40:30.448 --> 40:30.992
(Memorial tablet of Xu Wanzhou)

42:16.393 --> 42:17.192
Master.

42:18.353 --> 42:19.313
You woke up?

42:20.632 --> 42:21.712
Are you alright?

42:21.913 --> 42:23.353
Are you feeling unwell?

42:23.632 --> 42:24.433
I...

42:26.353 --> 42:27.152
Master.

42:28.232 --> 42:30.793
You fainted in the mansion last night.

42:34.313 --> 42:38.473
What were you doing
at Xu Wanzhou's courtyard, Master?

42:39.112 --> 42:39.913
I...

42:41.632 --> 42:43.072
I heard the sound of the zither.

42:46.224 --> 42:48.048
(Preview)

42:48.993 --> 42:51.152
Will Your Highness
be back for dinner today?

42:51.672 --> 42:52.712
Do you need something?

42:52.752 --> 42:54.632
I invited my senior brother over.

42:55.712 --> 42:58.112
Will you come back and dine with us?

42:58.473 --> 43:00.953
Your Highness, let me treat your legs.

43:01.272 --> 43:03.873
You do have sensation in your legs.

43:04.752 --> 43:08.033
What makes you think you can help me?

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
